content: Needs a English Translation ASAP, otherwise decent game.
I wont say why i love the game because its the same as others comments. The only this i need is English.
Looking foward for English Translation. My Chinese is too basic to understand what is inside. But overall I enjoyed the experience so far and the language is my only current issue.
It's a great game ...but ...I don't understand the language ... please help

Played the game for 20 minutes so far, but I can already see that the idea and its execution are WAY better than I expected. Love how the controls are handled (very in keeping with the theme of the game). Best wuxia game I've played on mobile, by far.
Great game it's very challenging once you get to the higher difficulties I just wish there was more customization and that you can fully customize your opponent as well
Keep the realism, and also add translations. This game have big potentials. Add LAN too.
I realy hope you can have a setting for other translation
The game is fun please add more characters and swords and add some more combos or add some techniques like wind, fire or something like that anyways love the game
Game is great but please add a feature to change the language!. Or if the feature is there already please walk me through it.
Really liked the game. Please add support for English.
Love this game, please add more gameplay for 弈剑
